Package: scc-lcd-daemon
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Nikhil Pagote <nikhil.pagote@gmail.com>
Depends: pciutils
Recommends: wireplumber, curl
Description: Front-panel LCD driver for Minisforum/AtomMan mini PCs
 Linux replacement for the Windows-only SCC front-panel LCD driver.
 Streams live CPU, GPU, memory, SSD, fan RPM and network transfer rates
 to the case's front status display, and applies volume changes made from
 the panel's own touch control.
 .
 Runs as a system service under root, which is required to read fan RPM
 and the CPU/GPU temperatures from the vendor embedded controller via
 direct port I/O, and to open the i915 perf PMU for GPU utilisation.
